author: @Patapom3
text: This feels like sticking together pieces of narrow models and attach them with duct tape and see how it fares... I'm afraid a model with 100 billion parameters won't perform as well as a system that is a bit better designed and that uses high level symbolic representations. It's high time we concentrate on a different architecture instead of doing more of the same.
